rem Cheap Hotel
rem 8/18/2017

items end table
items sofa

do Examine Cheap Hotel
 [
  print Behind a desk, this hotel is ran by a busy attendant. He doesn't pay any
  setflag seen attendant
  ifflag oldman gone
   [
    ifitemin hotel pass,INV
     [
      print attention to you as he organizes paperwork. There's an end table next
      print to a sofa, sparsely decorating this place.
     |
      print attention to you as he organizes paperwork. The sofa sits along the back
      print wall, next to it sits an end table with a hotel pass on it.
     ]
   |
    print attention to you as he organizes paperwork. On a sofa there's an old man
    print thinking to himself. Next to the sofa is an end table.
   ]
 ]

ifflag seen attendant
 [
  do Talk To Attendant
   [
    print "Can't you see I'm buried up to my balls in paperwork, go bother someone else."
   ]
 |]

ifflag oldman gone
 [|
  ifflag seen attendant
   [
    do Examine Old Man
     [
      print The old man is Japanese, sits on the couch, and holds on to a hotel pass
      print in his lap. He has a long beard that he slowly pulls on, thinking to
      print himself.
      setflag seen oldman
     ]
   |]
   
  ifflag seen oldman
   [
    do Talk To Old Man
     [
      print The old man looks at you, "Do you think we live in a simulation?"
      go Old Man
     ]
   |]
 ]

ifitemin hotel pass,INV
 [
  ifflag show pass
   [
    do Go Upstairs
     [
      print You walk up the stairs finding the first coffin your pass operates, then
      print climb into the narrow space.
      go Coffin
     ]
   |]
 |]

do Exit Cheap Hotel
 [
  print You leave the lobby, stepping back down into the street.
  go Outside Hotel
 ]